<P>But what changes can be made to the class to manage a specific role for us all.</P>
<P><BR>Well, let's help them out,&nbsp; this isn't a thread for piss-and-moan tactics...&nbsp; If we want to make it better, let's give the developers solid, c&#111;nstructive input.&nbsp; Let's bring in hard data to compare our class with others.&nbsp; We need input from characters of all levels.</P>
<P>Since we're a melee class let's focus &#111;n comparing our M&#111;nk Capabilities to the other melees... Hard data every&#111;ne... Parsing DPS at a variety of levels with appropriate weap&#111;nry, those of you who have melee alts at different levels of play, parse their DPS outputs also... This way we see proof of where the m&#111;nk is at all levels of advancement...&nbsp; <BR>Same goes for tankability... provide your AC/HP info, and how well/or not your Damage Avoidance/Mitigati&#111;n comes into play...</P>
<P><BR>Whining gets us nowhere, just lets us wallow in our misery... this will require a solid effort &#111;n the part of many m&#111;nks to get the data needed.</P><!-- Message body ''"" --></td>
