                    <td class="text" valign="top"><!-- Message body --><P>Agreed.</P>
<P>Make more readily available the weap&#111;ns that let us do our job. If soe sees us as an all area damage dealer, then give us the tools to do that. </P>
<P>For a m&#111;nk the best weap&#111;ns are very unobtainable. The easiest (relativly speaking) is the T-staff. 29/30 with the stun 120p dd proc. Cost 40kpp.&nbsp; very rare drop, and m&#111;nks normally have to roll for them against people who just plan &#111;n selling them. And nothing really compares to the epic for h2h that isnt acheived in a raid situati&#111;n (Fangs, SoM for examples)</P>
<P>&#079;n the flip side, I have a twinky warrior that is weilding a lammy/silken whip of ensnaring. Thats a 9/19 1hs with some minor stats and a whip thats 14/28 that procs snare. Argent defender for 2hs (33/49), and a centi warspear 20/30. I got all of these for under 4kpp. So ive equiped a warrior for for 1/10th the price of a t-staff</P>
<P>Now that the m&#111;nk community has pretty much accepted the nerf, and realize that they will not fix the nerf (despite what s&#111;ny says), I think that upping the damage we induce should be the focus</P>
